### ============================
### 🚀 ORDERS API
### ============================

### ➕ Create an Order (replace CUSTOMER_ID with a real ID)
POST http://localhost:5000/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "68d5536624b4e564e3939062",
  "product": "lollipop",
  "quantity": 100,
  "price": 200,
  "status": "Pending"
}

### 📄 Get All Orders
GET http://localhost:5000/orders

### 📄 Get Orders by Customer ID
GET http://localhost:5000/orders/customer/68d5536624b4e564e3939062

### ✏️ Update Order (replace ORDER_ID with real ID)
PUT http://localhost:5000/orders/68d5536624b4e564e3939062
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Shipped"
}

### ❌ Delete Order (replace ORDER_ID with real ID)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/orders/68d5536624b4e564e3939062

